INSERT INTO `ftgg_page` VALUES (38, '工程做货', '', '', '', '<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<img src="/Uploads/201405/536e283141454.jpg" title="做货" alt="做货" height="250" width="610" /><br />\r\n<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;"><br />\r\n</span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;">一．做货信息确认：<span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;">公司必须在收到客户的正式订购单或共同签定的订货合同进行确认后，以转化为相关的要求资料按公司系统执行生产及跟踪。<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span>&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;">二．做货周期<span>:</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;">根椐不同产品的生产特点，加工及材料要求等，以及公司当前的生产计划需要<span>3</span>个工作日<span>/7</span>个工作日<span>/12</span>个工作日<span>/15</span>个工作日不同阶段及交货周期等。<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span>&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;">三．做货跟踪<span>:</span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;">我司的会有专业的跟单人员跟进客户相关产品的生产情况及进度状况<span>,</span>并将相关的情况反馈给客户<span>,</span>除我司业务及业务跟单人员外<span>,</span>其它如品质工程等部门人员不参与客户货品生产的直接沟通与联络。<span></span></span>\r\n</p>', '', 0);
